(10163, 'Salibet oint. 30 gm', 'ساليبت مرهم 30 جرام', '19', '29', 'Betamethasone+salicylic acid', 'Jamjoom pharmaceuticals', 'Oint', 'مرهم', '', 'Glucocorticoid with keratolytic', '30 gm', 'uses: this medication is used to treat certain skin conditions. this product contains a corticosteroid called betamethasone (for swelling redness and itch) and a drug to help remove rough patches of skin. how to use: apply a thin layer to the affected are', '6281263176587', '', 4017, '2024-10-23', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
